    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a dependable commuter for someone who prioritizes function over aesthetics. The exterior shows its age with some paint fading on the hood and a few minor door dings from tight parking lots. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows some staining on the driver's seat, and the air conditioning takes a few minutes to reach full cooling capacity. Mechanically, it starts every time and has a consistent service history, though it will likely need new brake pads within the next few thousand miles.",
      "price": 18500.0,
